In this tutorial we will be create short curt for eclipse

First create the shortcurt, all shortcurt was on /usr/share/applications/ and have extension .desktop

sudo vim /usr/share/applications/eclipse.desktop
insert next lines:
[Desktop Entry]
Name=Eclipse
Comment=Eclipse
Exec=/opt/eclipse/eclipse
Icon=/opt/eclipse/icon.xpm
Terminal=false
Type=Application

save and out
ready we will have our shortcurt :D

